Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she a transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She looks so elegant and mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe some of you are forgetting how impolite it is to stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Knight Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you do, our knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to surprise you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you explored the school grounds yet, Kisakinomiya Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, how do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kajiura-sensei told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanahara Kaoruko from 3-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same dormitory building as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just Kaoruko is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:03:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, none of the students actually call it "Seio Girls' Academy."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just say "the school" or "Seio."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're a bit different from other schools, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it's too early for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the word for something that doesn't follow social norms?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherworldly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people call it a greenhouse too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, in both good and bad ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Students must be in class before the bell rings and be ready to start class once it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that rule already, \NNanahara Kaoruko-san, Kisakinomiya Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies, Kajiura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisakinomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could get used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mother put you in my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In this case, you have to pay attention to the process, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please translate the second chapter and turn it in the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Class dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are your parents foreigners?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My grandmother is a westerner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for prying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that you're so fluent in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not particularly fluent in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that all I've ever done is studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can translate the whole second chapter easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I could tutor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about tomorrow after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, are you already asking her out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't do that, Kaoruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't cheat on homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were eavesdropping, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were speaking so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kamichika Kaori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also lives in our dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's Kisakinomiya Chihaya-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is only her first day, \Nbut she's already the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose it is unusual to have \Nsomeone transfer in their senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, my hair is silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san, don't bully her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only jealous because you \Ndidn't take long to get close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh, stop teasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's head back to the dormitory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a drizzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, mist-like drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dormitory isn't far. We can run there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're drenched! You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up. If you stay out here, you'll get hypothermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I call Hatsune from the dormitory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we should get her inside first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She—I mean Yuu-san, is quite light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-chan, what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know very well about your own condition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to keep your body warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's move to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, she should know that \NHatsune-oneesama would be worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-san didn't eat her breakfast today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not introducing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kudo Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisakinomiya Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hinata-san, whom should I ask for\N permission to use the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, you don't need to ask to use the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuu-chan, you won't get better if you don't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you feel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much to ask, would you like to eat dessert together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called Eaton Mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a traditional dessert from Eaton College, England.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a mixture of strawberry, cream, and pieces of baked meringue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look like cherry blossom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bon appétit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful, Chihaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've been able to talk so much with Yuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I did was bring her a dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen her ask for seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko, you're doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko-san, did you catch a cold too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She just has a habit of staring at people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought that you were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, you even knew how to make sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the embodiment of what a lady should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it looks like she's sunk her fangs into you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a fever after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Hatsune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my honor to be praised by someone like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At Seio, underclassmen are to assist their seniors as a little sister would assist her elders,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it is an upperclassman's job is to guide her juniors like an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'm your "little sister" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Little sister"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I served you as your maid back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will continue to serve you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, I've prepared everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time for your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other girls have finished bathing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need not worry about them seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}An ideal lady, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long will you shut yourself in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you just transfer to Seio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some fine ladies go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Mom, that's not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Kajiura Hisako-san to push through the transfer for you, since she's the acting principal at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, like I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're charming, no one will notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, that's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}Seio is an all-girls school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a boy, for Pete's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't going to work out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Fumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is my job to do my best to ensure \Nthat you have a good time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, you're a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the mere sight of my tiny figure excites you so,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it will be impossible for you to spend your time safely here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you must get used to a girl's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumi, some—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that it's also important for you to learn this sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Your breasts... Your breasts, they're touching my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go that far, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The aroma of cape jasmine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-oneesama, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, wipe your tears. Don't let anyone see you crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did we dazzle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't you greet me, Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you can tell the others that \Nthe rumors about me were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you and sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that you're a bit \Ndifferent from the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a bit different myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I will live true to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, Kaori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a bit unique and the way she like to tease others is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, she's a good person on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she'd be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About how you want to learn more about her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors about her spread around often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful, good at just about everything, and you even show concern for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not that perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm envious of you too, for how \Nstraightforward and easygoing you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's continue studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}I'm kind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get homesick already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaori—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it, you're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it wouldn't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't protest, even if I am expelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that is your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you could be so honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you'd follow such \Nan absurd order from your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My tea isn't as good as Fumi's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I made you a simple herb tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Maroon Blue, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only is the color beautiful, \Nbut it will also warm up your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you asking how I figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember how cautious you were about touching when we first met?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, you lifted Yuu easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how light Yuu is, it's no simple task for a girl to lift another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Through the eyes of a girl, you were too perfect,\N if only because that's the role you were playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there were a few other things that\N I don't think anybody besides me noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also told me that you wouldn't expose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going to expose me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Personally, I think it's okay for you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I think it'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you've discovered me on my secret\N rendezvous with her, I think you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also stand to gain something from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko-san, could I have a moment with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko, who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's Kisakinomiya Chihaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a new tenant in our dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kelly Grandselius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am the night itself, the princess who wields the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Venus and Pluto have made a spectrum, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that you were born under unfortunate stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kelly, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2A0249&\an8}Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're closing soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you wondering whether Kaoruko has figured out that you're a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say this as a matter of fact, not to flatter you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you're a perfect girl on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone except me has figured out that you're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried, then maybe you could act less perfect in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. I was just a little uneasy, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chihaya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya, would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I win, you'll tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first one to land a clean hit is the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll end this match in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Faire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are really you a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must think that I'm acting odd now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:19:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoruko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're thinking or what you're planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might not believe me, but\N this is something that I must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, since you've discovered my identity, I'll have to leave Seio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think that'll solve everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you fool us with such halfhearted feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'll test you using my reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Commence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does lying come naturally to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you fool us with such halfhearted feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even involved Kaori-san! \NWhat were you trying to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what were you trying to do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what do you think, Kaoruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still can't forgive him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've calmed down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all about camouflage and imaging tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll become my ally, in return I'll protect his secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you accepting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Yuu-chan would be sad if you suddenly left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I kind of admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, you look like my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I must say that it makes me a bit furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I don't think it'd be a bad idea if you stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya-sama, wipe your tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are tears of happiness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're happy that you can watch \Ngirls undress for the next year, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3E2451&\an8}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right, changing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you can keep going to this school \Ndespite being found out by two girls in the first few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumi believes this to be a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last time in PE, you...
